{"tid":2329776,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：譚文豪罰王宗堯做店長（李八方）","createTime":"2020-12-17T12:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T13:36:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"83e9bc81c3a50ff22bfd025c33f894897250556f","tid":2329776,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:42:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/2FIIXYSRWFGNBJWUA5LAPJMTSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F2FIIXYSRWFGNBJWUA5LAPJMTSQ%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28QEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=17ff5604\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F2FIIXYSRWFGNBJWUA5LAPJMTSQ%2F&h=86ce2049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/2FIIXYSRWFGNBJWUA5LAPJMTSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：譚文豪罰王宗堯做店長（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n一方有難，八方支援。因去年7.1闖立會案，被控暴動及進入或逗留在立法會會議廳範圍兩罪嘅藝人王宗堯（Greg），噚日喺網上公開請求大家「懲罰」，以應付可能達七位數嘅律師費後，唔少黃店即時大力「懲罰」。過去多次為黃店做一日店長、近日成為茶記「一日三餐」老闆嘅公民黨副主席譚文豪，宣佈「高薪挖角」王宗堯噚日去佢間舖做一日店長，呼籲黃色經濟圈嘅同路人，有咩商業合作機會都可以支持下Greg。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0qo7QM-u-grg-XuZS2nHht6fdDI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NQUQI2FKKZBS7GHOLS7MDMLB4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0qo7QM-u-grg-XuZS2nHht6fdDI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNQUQI2FKKZBS7GHOLS7MDMLB4M.jpg&h=f9b4d405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■譚文豪搵咗王宗堯去佢間茶記做一日店長，身體力行支持同路人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換圍裙落單包外賣<br />\n<br />\nGreg噚日中午現身茶餐廳，即時換上圍裙開工，喺舖內招待客人、清潔、包外賣乜都做，佢又同譚文豪到店外同客人講多謝同影相，客人一句句嘅「加油」、「頂住呀」，令Greg好感動，仲有一名女士塞錢畀譚文豪，叫佢轉交Greg，但俾佢哋婉拒。<br />\n<br />\nGreg提到有市民希望捐錢幫佢，佢話𠵱家搞眾籌有一定危險，所以佢情願用有尊嚴方式賺錢，再用啲錢去做需要做嘅嘢，至於擔唔擔心有客戶受壓而唔敢搵佢？Greg話搵得佢嘅客戶理念都好堅定，又話已知律師費條數大概幾多，所以想盡做唔靠人。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"dfc76c1a569ffeafaa3eaa79f1d4985f5397e1ac","tid":2329776,"uid":43204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b37157646cbab2643af13bda47588ccc858a427","tid":2329776,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc76c1a569ffeafaa3eaa79f1d4985f5397e1ac","tid":2329776,"uid":43204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068a25e7bf5e18e2c7801f7953194e92ae20805c","tid":2329776,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"但成百萬計既律師費<br />\n你攪呢D一年都賺唔到啦<br />\n直接賣簽名相大家去買咁就易做好多"},{"pid":"10dbde094cba62de8c699cd5fdb465697d21c184","tid":2329776,"uid":322110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068a25e7bf5e18e2c7801f7953194e92ae20805c","tid":2329776,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"但成百萬計既律師費<br />\n你攪呢D一年都賺唔到啦<br />\n直接賣簽名相大家去買咁就易做好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"希望佢快d賣嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce07f771356b67010d49f615ee6cf679fc767d6","tid":2329776,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T13:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e1FPBQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe1FPBQP.png&h=f712d772&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d17de7dbfadb4528435d806271d4ba63bec926b","tid":2329776,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10dbde094cba62de8c699cd5fdb465697d21c184","tid":232977